      <div class="services-grid">
        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon">
            <img src="hearts.png" alt="Connection Icon" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="service-title">Connection</h3>
          <p class="service-description">
            True connection with ourselves and the Divine comes when we fully
            recognize our emotions and the wisdom they bring. Instead of looking
            for the Divine outside of us, we realize that it's already woven
            into every part of us—our emotions, bodies, and inner knowing. By
            allowing ourselves to feel and honor our emotions, we become more in
            touch with our true selves, which opens the door to a deeper
            connection with the Divine. The more we understand and accept
            ourselves, the more we can clearly hear and follow the guidance that
            comes from within.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon">
            <img src="/triangles.svg" alt="Alignment Icon" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="service-title">Alignment</h3>
          <p class="service-description">
            Spiritual alignment is about living in true harmony with
            yourself—where your emotions, body, and spirit are in sync, and your
            thoughts, feelings, and actions reflect your deepest values. It's
            the clarity and confidence that comes from being fully connected to
            your inner guidance and authentic self. When you're aligned, you
            allow your emotions to flow, trust the process of life, and
            surrender to what's unfolding. This deep connection leads you toward
            your soul's purpose, bringing you lasting peace, joy, and
            fulfillment.
          </p>
          <p class="service-description">
            Imagine living in a way that feels effortless, authentic, and true
            to who you are. Spiritual alignment helps you tune into your
            emotions and inner wisdom, guiding you toward a life that's not only
            meaningful but deeply aligned with your highest potential.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon">
            <img src="/person.png" alt="Embodiment Icon" class="person" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="service-title">Embodiment</h3>
          <p class="service-description">
            Spiritual embodiment involves allowing oneself to fully experience
            and feel emotions in their entirety. Rather than suppressing,
            avoiding, or numbing difficult emotions, this approach encourages
            giving them the space to surface and flow. In doing so, we honor the
            natural movement of feelings, which, when allowed to fully express,
            can bring deeper clarity and healing. Emotions, in this sense, are
            not obstacles to our spiritual or emotional growth, but are
            essential signals that guide us back to greater alignment with our
            deepest inner wisdom and authentic self-expression.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

