          dynamics profoundly shape individual well-being and the healing
          process.
        </p>

        <p class="about-text">
          Yet, my truest growth has blossomed through a lifelong commitment to
          inner work. As I embarked on my own journey of emotional healing and
          self-discovery, I realized that to guide others authentically, I
          needed to embody the transformation I wished to inspire. This
          dedication to personal evolution remains at the core of my practice,
          infusing my work with empathy, presence, and insight.
        </p>

        <p class="about-text">
          With this foundation of education, clinical experience, and personal
